column5: A friend of mine has an excavator that he bought used, all the labels in it are in Japanese and he'd like to get a rough translation of what they mean. I have photos of them and will post or email them if anyone thinks they might be able to translate them into English. Sure would be appreciated!  If you want, you can email me @ [email protected]
Hi Cliff. please send then to me by e-mail and I will see what I can do. Might take me a week or so.......
Please to check PM's Cliff san.
こんにちはクリフ  私は助けることができない。 私は日本の単語を話すことはありません
